# GPU fast + accuracy profile

Canonical runtime values live in [`../docker/gpu-app.env`](../docker/gpu-app.env)
(loaded by all NVIDIA compose stacks under `deploy/docker/`).

Summary:
- Keep `DIARIZATION_ACCURACY_MODE=true` and locked thresholds
- Faster long-audio path via larger diar windows / smaller overlap
- Turn-guided ASR up to 28s slices; beams=4; `ASR_FAST_MODE=true`
